OL,3,CMum of schoolgirl who died at
OL,4,Cpsychiatric unit welcomes new guidance
OL,6,FThe mother of a 12-year-old girl, who
OL,7,Ftook her own life in a mental health
OL,8,Funit after her rare brain disorder was
OL,9,Fmissed by doctors, has welcomed new
OL,10,Fguidance on the condition.
OL,12,FMia Lucas, from Nottingham, died in
OL,13,FJanuary 2024 after she was sectioned
OL,14,Fat the Becton Centre in Sheffield
OL,15,Fthree weeks after being moved there
OL,16,Ffrom the Queen's Medical Centre (QMC)
OL,17,Fin Nottingham.
