OL,3,CMum of schoolgirl who died at
OL,4,Cpsychiatric unit welcomes new guidance
OL,6,FAn inquest into her death last year
OL,7,Fheard medical professionals at QMC
OL,8,Ffailed to identify a disorder called
OL,9,Fautoimmune encephalitis, a swelling of
OL,10,Fthe brain which caused her acute
OL,11,Fpsychosis but could have been treated.
OL,13,FThe jury found it "possibly
OL,14,Fcontributed" to her death.
