OL,3,CMum of schoolgirl who died at
OL,4,Cpsychiatric unit welcomes new guidance
OL,6,FNow, in response to a Prevention of
OL,7,FFuture Deaths report from the coroner,
OL,8,Fthe Royal College of Psychiatry has
OL,9,Fconfirmed it will release national
OL,10,Fclinical guidance on autoimmune
OL,11,Fencephalitis and autoimmune psychosis
OL,12,Fwithin the next six months.
OL,14,FMia's mother Chloe Hayes said: "While
OL,15,FI am pleased to see that new guidance
OL,16,Fis being developed, this will always
OL,17,Fbe hugely difficult for me as all this
OL,18,Fcomes too late for Mia.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
