OL,3,CMum of schoolgirl who died at
OL,4,Cpsychiatric unit welcomes new guidance
OL,6,FThe trust is currently conducting an
OL,7,Finvestgation into Mia's care which is
OL,8,Fexpected to conclude later this year.
OL,10,FChloe is urging NHS England to make
OL,11,Fchanges quickly.
OL,13,FShe said: "No family should have to
OL,14,Flose a child to bring about changes in
OL,15,Fhow known conditions are treated, and
OL,16,FIt breaks my heart that meaningful
OL,17,Faction is only being taken now, after
OL,18,FMia has died.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
