OL,3,CMum of schoolgirl who died at
OL,4,Cpsychiatric unit welcomes new guidance
OL,6,F"If stronger awareness, clearer
OL,7,Fguidance, and more urgent action had
OL,8,Fbeen in place sooner, my daughter
OL,9,Fwould still be here today.
OL,11,F"I truly hope that we will see changes
OL,12,Fnow made as soon as possible so that
OL,13,Fother children are accurately
OL,14,Fassessed, listened to, and protected.
OL,16,F"I don't want another family to live
OL,17,Fwith the excruciating pain that we now
OL,18,Fcarry every single day."
